  "original_title": "\u0d9a\u0ddc\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dd4 \u0db0\u0dd3\u0dc0\u0dbb \u0dbb\u0dd0\u0d9a\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dcf \u0dc3\u0db3\u0dc4\u0dcf \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0db7\u0dcf\u0d9c \u0db4\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dc0\u0dda\u0dc2\u0db4\u0dad\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb \u0db1\u0dd2\u0d9a\u0dd4\u0dad\u0dca \u0d9a\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0dd3\u0db8 \u0d87\u0dbb\u0db9\u0dda",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Issuance of examination admit cards for Korean fishing jobs begins",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The issuance of exam tickets for the Korean Language Proficiency Test to be held in the year 2022 for jobs in the fishing industry in South Korea will be done online from 22.08.2022 to 26.08.2022.",
        "The tickets required for the examination will be issued through the official website of Sri Lanka Foreign Employment Bureau www.slbfe.lk.",
        "Applicants who have obtained the examination papers for the language proficiency examination in the production sector held in the year 2022 will not have an opportunity to apply for this. Individuals between the ages of 18-39 can apply, who are not colorblind, who have not been incarcerated or convicted of serious crimes, and who have no previous records of deportation by South Korea.",
        "Application form, scanned copy of passport, scanned copy of 3.5 cm \u00d7 4.5 cm photograph taken within 3 months and receipt of payment of examination fee of Rs.10,108 are required to get the exam admit cards.",
        "The language proficiency test required for jobs in the fishing industry will be held from October 5 to November 30, 2022 through computer. More information regarding this examination and examination ticket issuance can be obtained through the official website of the Bureau www.slbfe.lk."
      ],
